FBIS4-40810 "drsov119_a_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-119 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Envoy Says DPRK `Ready' Envoy Says DPRK `Ready' LD2006143394 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 1400 GMT 20 Jun 94 LD2006143394 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] North Korea is ready for a third round of talks on the nuclear problem, the DPRK ambassador in Moscow stated today at a closed sitting of the Russian State Duma's Committee for International Affairs. The ambassador said abandonment of the imposition of economic sanctions against the DPRK is a condition for talks to begin.
